    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Transfer of heat from one point to another due to the tendency of heat to flow from an area of higher temperature to an area of lower temperature.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
